column5: Fellow Fisherman, I would love to hear some fishing storys about Canada from you. Please email me your favorite TRUE story. I want to put them in a book and I will send each story teller a copy of the completed book. There has to be some great storys among this many fisherman. Look forward to hearing from you....Thanks..................walleyewacker1@yaho o.com
Just sent you my favorite story. Had a Bear in camp for a week and he ate good.
